<!--pages/recruitment/recruitment.wxml-->
<view class="mid">
  <view class='row-text'>
    <scroll-view scroll-y='true' style="height: 200px;" scroll-top="{{position}}" bindscrolltolower='finish' scroll-with-animation='true'>
      <view class="container"><text>Hello,19级的萌新们</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>首先恭喜你们在南开建校百年之际</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>加入我们这个温暖的大家庭</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>作为南开大学团委服务中心的线上宣传部门</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>我们想对每一位点开这个程序的幸运儿</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>做一个简单的了解</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>如果你也想知道自己是否与我们五行相合</text></view>
      <view class="container"><text>那就快点开始吧</text></view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>
  <!-- <view class="block" hidden="{{showtext}}"></view> -->
  <view style="width:100%;" hidden='{{!showtext}}'>
    <view class='container'>
      <button class='bar-button half' hover-class='bar-button__hover' bindtap='starttest'>参与测试</button>
    </view>
    <view class='container'>
      <button class='bar-button half' hover-class='bar-button__hover' bindtap='exit'>退出</button>
    </view>
    <view class='container'>
      <button class='bar-button half' hover-class='bar-button__hover' open-type='share'>分享小程序</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
